{"tid":1379974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《環球時報》總編：若香港力量不夠用　国家力量隨時可以協助","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T01:58:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4b162cf63b4cf61215cfaae482474323c1882932","tid":1379974,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進發表文章，指香港激進示威者氣焰囂張，局勢相當緊張，又形容本來是反修例的示威，現在要徹底癱瘓政府。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進在微博提到，激進示威者不斷高呼「光復香港，時代革命」的極端口號，指這時候喊「革命」，越來越有「顏色革命」的味道，而「光復香港」讓人想到的，也不再是「反水客」的簡單主張，讓人想到的就是「港獨」。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進指，如果示威者的顏色革命全面暴力化，物極必反，一定會遭到嚴厲痛擊，香港的力量如果不夠用，國家的力量隨時可以協助。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471054-20190729.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471054-20190729.htm&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy0zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=3331c9b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471054-20190729.htm&h=639147cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471054-20190729.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7e221f3cb432c7ee36930c89dba60db936764523","tid":1379974,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:55:31.000Z","msg":"佢意思係香港快d叫中共出兵 中共唔想再見到咁"},{"pid":"1a57bad36e4526bb8f5bb17f3ebd4e35cd16913b","tid":1379974,"uid":140552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:57:38.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"b29750f8dd261fa31f0c97a42c297fe67aa380bc","tid":1379974,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:58:47.000Z","msg":"等到好眼訓zzzz"}]}